body: Soo its acting very weird.I cant se most of the text,i cant type my username or password.I just cant login.I dont know what else to say but for you to look at this ss i made

replies.body:
That's really weird! You're most likely seeing this as a result of missing/corrupt files in the League directory. I recommend running a repair by hitting the cog icon in the top-right and hitting the button for *Initiate full repair*. 

Let me know if this helped!
